# ===== Experiment artifact exclusions =====
# Model weights & optimizer states (too large for git)
*.safetensors
*.pt
# Auto-generated tokenizer copies (11MB each)
**/distill_runs/**/tokenizer.json
**/distill_runs/**/chat_template.jinja
# Auto-generated PEFT README & small config copies in every checkpoint
**/distill_runs/**/outputs/**/README.md
**/distill_runs/**/outputs/**/adapter_config.json
**/distill_runs/**/outputs/**/tokenizer_config.json
# Root-level training logs (not needed in repo)
/*.log
# Temp diagnostic files
external_model_benchmark_20260326/file_sizes_*.tsv
# Benchmark leaderboard outputs (auto-generated, can be re-run)
external_model_benchmark_20260326/outputs/
# Checkpoint dirs that only contain model weights (caught by *.safetensors *.pt but keep dir clean)
**/output_seed*/checkpoints/